'''四巫日'''（{{lang-en|Quadruple witching day}}）是指[[美國|美國]]股市於每年三月、六月、九月和十二月的第三个星期五，是[[衍生性金融商品|衍生性金融商品]]到期結算日。當日最後交易小時稱為'''四巫小時'''（{{lang-en|Quadruple witching hour}}），為[[紐約|紐約]]時間下午三時至四時。

到期結算的商品共有四類，故稱四巫日：
* [[股票指數期貨|股票指數期貨]]
* [[股票指數選擇權|股票指數選擇權]]
* [[期權|期權]]
* [[股票期貨|個股期貨]]

因[[2002年|2002年]][[11月8日|11月8日]]起，美國市場才開始交易[[個股期貨|個股期貨]]，故在此之前稱為'''三巫日'''（{{lang-en|Triple witching day}}）或'''三巫小時'''（{{lang-en|Triple witching hour}}）。<ref>{{cite web |title=Quadruple Witching |url=http://www.investopedia.com/terms/q/quadruplewitching.asp |publisher=Investopedia |access-date=2021-03-19 |archive-date=2021-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210618124213/https://www.investopedia.com/terms/q/quadruplewitching.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://hitandruncandlesticks.com/what-is-triple-witching/ |title=What is triple witching? |last1=Saddler |first1=Rick |date=2014-06-25 |website=Hit & Run Candlesticks |publisher= |access-date=2016-07-01 |quote=This daylong event, which is sometimes referred to as “Freaky Friday,” is an important day for short-term investors because the markets tend to be turbulent and unpredictable, shifting erratically as traders attempt to offset their orders before the closing bell rings. |archive-date=2020-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105053149/https://hitandruncandlesticks.com/what-is-triple-witching/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

